        <num>CC 597</num>
        <heading>597.  Liability of the usufructuary for servitudes</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 597.  Liability of the usufructuary for servitudes.
The usufructuary who loses a predial servitude by nonuse or who permits a servitude to be acquired on the property by prescription is responsible to the naked owner.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110789</p>
        </authorialNote>
